com.layers.app.model

Class Scale

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.layers.app.model.Liquor
      • com.layers.app.model.Scale
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestScale

    public class Scale
extends Liquor
implements java.io.Serializable

    Scale model is used to emmulate the actual Arduino Scale on site. Scales can be configured to liquors. Also used for logging information and history of scale use.

    Extends liquor model so this single object can contain the liquor object configured to it. Serialized to support HTTP POST json to model conversion.

    Fields: ( ex: [access-modifier] name : type {validation} ) 
    # locationId : String {0-20}
    # scaleId : int {0-5}
    # liquorCode : String {5-20}
    # logQuantity : float {0-1500}
    # logMessage : String {0-1000}
    # logTime : Timestamp
